sources.description:
*Roadkill* Lost while traveling through a rural county in 1983, a young woman crosses paths with a hitchhiker headed the same destination and offers a ride in exchange for directions.  Their journey takes a violent turn when the two are caught up in a police manhunt for a fugitive killer.   As victims begin to amass and authorities close in, it becomes a fight for survival on the open road.   
2024.  Stars: Caitlin Carmichael, Ryan Knudson, Danielle Harris
